Class List

java.lang.Object
  ca.etsmtl.log430.lab1.List
Direct Known Subclasses:
ProjectList, ResourceList
public class List
extends java.lang.Object

This is the base class that is used to construct the various list objects used in this application. The storage mechanism used is the Java Vector found in the java.util package. A vector object is declared and several generic operations are defined for the List class.

Version:
1.4, 2013-Sep-13
Author:
A.J. Lattanze, CMU
